Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您就是弗伦迪先生？\n请您去接个电话，巴黎来的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Are you signor Ferrante?\nI have a telephone call for you from Paris.{\r}
