Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}喂？对，我是弗伦迪{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hello?\nYes, this is Ferrante.{\r}
