Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你好呀，加布里埃尔\n你少跟我废话{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"Hello, Gabriella."\nDon't you talk to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那你干吗打电话来呢？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Don't talk...\nthen why did you call me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你曾经说你爱我\n好话都让你说了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}How could you speak of love to me,\nsay the things you did?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}现在你要结婚了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And you,\nabout to be married!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你还记得我给你那个香烟盒时\n你说的话吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You remember what you whispered\nwhen I gave you the cigarette case?{\r}
