Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}喂！喂！\n你在听吗，加布里埃尔？\n电话好像断了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hello! Hello! Can you hear me, Gabriella?\nI believe we're disconnected.{\r}
