Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}接线员！接线员… 噢，真不像话，接线员！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Operator! Operat...\nOh, this is a shame. Operator!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}伪君子！若我手里有把刀…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hypocrite! I have in my hand a knife...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我就会插在你的背上{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and I wish it were\nin your back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hm.{\r}
