Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这个嘛…烟盒里有写给我的赠言{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well... There's an inscription to me on the inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是吗{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}“给尼古拉”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"To Nicolo."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！原来你就是大名鼎鼎的…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Don't tell me\nyou're the famous...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}关于你的报道我看多了\n《生活画报》上，还有…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I have read so much about you in,\nuh, Life and Look and...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}还有《好管家》上？\n可以把盒还给我吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Possibly Good Housekeeping?\nNow, may I have my case?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦不不，等一等  - 嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No, no. Just a moment.  - Hm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哇！关系可不一般啦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Whew! This is\nfrightfully intimate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}遗憾的是我的法语不行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I know just enough French\nto be embarrassed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你能不能简略一点儿\n告诉我写的是什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Could you, um, refine it a little\nand tell me in effect what it says?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那好吧，那上面说…呃…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, in effect, it says, uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}“加布里埃尔号上的三个难忘之夜留念”…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"In memory of three unforgettable nights\naboard La Gabriella"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她的私人游艇{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}which is her yacht.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}看来还真是你的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I guess that's you, all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你是不是写过“我不再微笑”这首歌？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Tell me, did you write the song,\n"I'll Never Smile Again"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}没有{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}但我在考虑写一首\n叫“月色笼罩加布里埃尔号”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But I'm thinking of writing one called\n"Moon Over La Gabriella."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您认为幽会能代替晚场棒球赛吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Do you think it will ever take the place\nof night baseball?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不会的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请等一等{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Please wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我遇到了很大的麻烦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm in trouble,\nserious trouble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢 到处幽会当然会出现麻烦\n可怜的姑娘{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I could've told you.\nPlaying around yachts. The poor thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我想跟你谈谈  - 这种事我可不太擅长{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I must talk with someone.  - Well, I'm not very good at that sort of thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我曾经很健谈，可这习惯我已经该了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I talk a lot.\nI've tried to break myself of the habit, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可你这张脸很诚实{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But you have\nsuch an honest face.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 是吗？  - 我可以信任你，是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I have?  - I can trust you, can't I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这倒是可以  - 太好了，跟我来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Yes, I suppose so.  - Good. Come with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可船长那张脸也是诚实的\n你干吗不去找他诉苦？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The captain has an honest face too.\nWhy can't you tell him your troubles?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 去我的客舱还是你的？  - 我的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Shall we go to your cabin or to mine?  - Ah, no, mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我的就在…  - 我的在这儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- But mine is just around the...  - Mine is here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不是我谨小慎微…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's not that\nI'm prudish...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是我妈妈告戒我\n千万不要单独进一个男人的房间{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}but my mother told me never to enter\na man's room in months ending in "R."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She did?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哎，哦，这么说你母亲不仅漂亮，而且聪明{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ah. Oh, well, your mother's\nnot only beautiful, she's clever too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你叫什么？  - 特瑞·麦凯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- What is your name?  - Terry McKay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}特瑞·麦凯，独自一个人旅行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Terry McKay,\nand I'm traveling alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 是不是这事在烦呢？  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Was that, by any chance,\nwhat was troubling you?  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 可以吗？  - 可以{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- May I?  - You may.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃…放在这儿就行了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Um... I think you can leave it here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢 这事太巧了，你救了我一命{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, this couldn't be nicer.\nYou saved my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我都快烦死了\n起程以后我在船上一个漂亮女人都没有看见{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I was bored. I hadn't seen one\nattractive woman on this ship since we left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我都惊呆了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now, isn't that terrible?\nI was alarmed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我不停地自问\n“漂亮女人都不出门儿了？”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I said to myself,\n"Don't beautiful women travel anymore?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}后来看见了你，但愿我这一下得救了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And then I saw you,\nand I was saved, I hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}告诉我，你是不是靠这套言辞赢得女人的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Tell me, have you been getting results\nwith a line like that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我一点儿也不感到惊奇？  - 你要是惊奇倒会令我惊奇{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Or would I be surprised?  - If you were surprised, I'd be surprised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你可真会挖苦人\n这种话我也能说一大堆{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That sounds like a nasty crack.\nI can make a few, too, if...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我相信你能  - 我当然能{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm sure you could.  - I know I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我已经说了  - 我也会说{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That's what I said.  - All right. I think I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我洗耳恭听  - 你未婚妻认识\n那个加布里埃尔号的女主角？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm listening.  - Does your fiancee know\nthe lady of the yacht, Gabriella?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}当然知道，她们俩是好朋友{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Why, certainly.\nShe's her best friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}要好的朋友{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Chummy little group.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我觉得这船走得太快了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, this ship is going much too fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}每一分钟都不能白白地浪费{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We ought to take advantage\nof every moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你，你不觉得生活应该欢快灿烂…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Uh, don't you think that life\nshould be gay and bright...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}就像冒泡的香槟吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and bubbly\nlike champagne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我喜欢粉色香槟  - 我就是那个意思…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I like pink champagne.  - That's the kind I mean... pink champagne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我们为什么不让这次旅途\n像粉色香槟那么美好？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Is there any reason why from now on\nthis trip shouldn't be pink champagne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯哼  - 怎么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mm-hmm.  - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，天啦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 他不赞成？  - 不{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- He wouldn't like it, hmm?  - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 丈夫？  - 不是{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Husband?  - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那他也不赞成？  - 不赞成{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- He still wouldn't like it?  - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那么 他为什么不和你一起来呢？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Uh, why isn't he\ntraveling with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 他得去德克萨斯办理公司合并的事 - 哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Because he had to go to Texas on a big merger.  - Ah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他建议在他去办那项生意期间\n我最好来趟旅行…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He thought it'd be a good idea if I took\na little trip while he consummated this deal...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}因为我对做生意一窍不通{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}because I have\nno head for business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我真是弄不明白 一个出现赤字的公司…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's beyond me how the more money\na corporation loses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}怎样才能做到亏损越多\n赚钱也越多{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}the more money it makes,\nbecause of the carryovers with the write-offs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你觉得就是让实力雄厚的大公司\n去吞并弱小的小公司…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The big secret seems to be to merge a sick\ncorporation with a big, fat, healthy one...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这样就都好起来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and then everybody gets well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不太好吧？  - 在这类事情上…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Silly, isn't it?  - He doesn't think I'm dumb...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他倒不认为我太笨\n也不觉得我太聪明{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}but, um, he doesn't think\nI'm very bright about things like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你本来就很聪明{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, it isn't necessary, is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 谢谢  - 没什么{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Thank you.  - That's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这么说他很信任你了？  - 绝对信任{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well... So he trusts you?  - Implicitly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯 没有过失、没有差错、没有闹过小误会…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm, no mistakes, no errors,\nno tiny little slips...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 绝对忠实的五年  - 哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Five faithful years.  - Ah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}难以置信吧，可这是真的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Sounds awful,\ndoesn't it, but it's true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是吗，原来是这样{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Well, there you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 抽吗？  - 不，谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Cigarette?  - No, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃，我怎么没带…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I don't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那段烫耳的赠言足以能够点着？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You could light it\nfrom that inscription, couldn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，说得妙，你说什么我都听着{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I like...\nI must stay tuned into you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是啊，哦，他…他可真走运\n一定是个出色的男子汉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Oh, he... he's a very lucky fellow.\nMust be a remarkable man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}当然啦\n像你这样迷人的男子我都能抵御…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, you can imagine\nhow attractive he is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可见他的魅力有多大了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}when I can resist\nso charming a person as, um...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是啊，哦，我懂了 我们交谈得很愉快？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Yes. Oh, I understand.\nWell, it was nice, wasn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}知道吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}甲板上能玩网球、智木盘，和拼纸牌{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, there's still deck tennis,\nshuffleboard, bingo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦 是不是让您觉得尴尬了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, don't tell me\nyou're embarrassed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，坦率地说很尴尬{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Yes, as a matter\nof fact, I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，真对不起  - 这没什么，用不着道歉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, I am sorry.  - It's all right. Don't apologize.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 但愿这事不会伤了你的自尊…\N- 哪儿能呢，想到哪儿去了，别这样想{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I do hope it won't affect your ego because...  - Don't think anything of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我带上我的自尊去散散步{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll just take\nmy ego for a walk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 当然，除非你愿意…  - 和你共进晚餐？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Unless, of course, you'd care to...  - Have dinner with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我当然愿意{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'd love to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}啊 我的朋友弗伦迪先生来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Here comes my friend\nFerrante now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}啊 弗伦迪先生\n这是我妹妹哈瑟维小姐…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mr. Ferrante, I'd like to have you meet\nmy sister, Miss Hathaway...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我妻子哈瑟维太太…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and my wife,\nMrs. Hathaway...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那么，呃，告诉我，你小的时候…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And, uh,\nwhen you were little...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}保姆在睡觉前给你念什么书？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}what did your nurse\nread to you at bedtime?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 让我想想…  - 是《卡萨诺瓦回忆录》吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Let me see...  - The memoirs of Casanova?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}每晚都念，然后我们就熄灯睡觉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Every night.\nAnd then we'd turn out the light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- “我们”？  - 那时我才这么点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- "We"?  - I was only so big.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你的童年一定非常快乐吧  - 哦，是这样{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You must've had a happy childhood.  - Ah, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 还有女人？  - 噢，女人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And women?  - Oh, women.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你认识的多极了，对吗？  - 哦，说不好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You've known quite a few, haven't you?  - Oh, I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 是不是“极”字用错了  - 是有点儿不太确切{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Or perhaps "few" is the wrong word.  - Let's say it's not precise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}打搅您了，弗伦迪先生{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I beg your pardon,\nsignor Ferrante.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这张桌子要不要每晚给您留着？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Would you like me to reserve this table\nfor you every night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 干吗不呢？  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Why not?  - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 刚才说哪儿了？  - 那些女人全都发疯似地爱上了您{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Now, where were we?  - And I suppose they've all\nbeen madly in love with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不一定  - 而您，对他们却不够尊重{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I doubt it.  - But, uh, you haven't had\nmuch respect for them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，恰恰相反…  - 不过您对他们的评介却很公平{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, on the contrary...\n- Still, you've always been very fair in your judgments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，最公平不过了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. I've been more than fair.\nI idealize them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我把他们视为偶像\n放在至高无上的位置{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Every woman I meet,\nI put up there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可认识时间一长，了解一深就…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Of course, the longer I know her\nand the better I know her...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 很难保住她们是不是？  - 是啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It's hard to keep them up there, isn't it?  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}很快偶像就摇晃了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Pretty soon,\nthe pedestal wobbles...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}没多久就倒塌了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and then topples.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}现实中就是这样{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}C'est la vie, et cetera.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不说了，来谈谈你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Come on.\nLet's talk about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，今晚不行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No. Not tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我的故事改天再讲{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We'll talk about me\nsome other time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 明天我正好没什么安排  - 噢，可我有{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- We've nothing planned for tomorrow.  - Oh, I have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，那不行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}明天就谈我，说定了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We'll talk about me tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢 天气真是好极了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It turned out\nbeautifully, didn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我都热了，谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's really warm.\nThank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}刚才说哪儿了？\n你要告诉我你的出生地{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now, where were we? You were\ngoing to tell me where you were born.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 就是这儿，那好…  - 弗伦迪先生？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That's right. Well...  - Mr. Ferrante?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 您的电报  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Cablegram.  - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请原谅，麦凯小姐{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Excuse me, Miss McKay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 麦凯小姐？  - 对，是我{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Miss McKay?  - Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 也有您的一封  - 哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I have one for you too.  - Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 谢谢  - 不客气{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Thank you.  - You're welcome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请原谅，弗伦迪先生{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Excuse me, Mr. Ferrante.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 他来的？  - 她来的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- From him?  - From her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯哼  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mm-hmm.  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃，刚才说到哪儿了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, uh, where were we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，说到我要告诉你我的出生地点…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I was about to tell you\nwhere I was born...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我嘛，出生在波士顿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and, um, I was born\nin Boston.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 快长大吧，我都等不及了  - 你耐心一点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I can hardly wait for you to grow up.  - Yes. Well, be patient.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我马上就长大{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I grew up quickly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我去了纽约\n在一家夜总会唱歌…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Then I went to New York and got a job...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}从晚十点到凌晨三点{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}singing in a nightclub\nfrom 10:00 to 3:00 in the morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}然后经理会纠缠我一个小时…四点钟{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The manager used to chase me around\nthe office until about 4:00 and then...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}下班回家{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I went home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 他有没有…  - 哦，没有  - 那就好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Did he ever, uh...  - Oh, no, no.  - is good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}后来一天晚上…他来找我{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, then one evening...\nhe came along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 呃，就是这家伙  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Ah. This is the fellow.  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他来对我说…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And, uh, he said, um...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}“你可不属于夜总会这种地方”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"You don't belong\nin a place like this."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 真的？  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Really?  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我就问他“是吗”？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And I said, uh, "I don't?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}啊哈，他就…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And, uh, well, then...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯？什么？  - 什么什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Hmm? What?  - What what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我以为你说了什么呢  - 我什么也没说{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I thought you said something.  - I didn't say anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}但你猜对了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But you're right, you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他说我属于\n花园大道的一间顶楼小屋…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He said I belonged\nin a penthouse on Park Avenue...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}每天尽情饱览东河的美景{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}with a breathtaking view\nof the East River.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你发奋努力的理想地方{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}An ideal place for you\nto improve yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}对，于是我就开始用功{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. So, I studied hard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}唱歌？…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Singing? And...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 学习音乐，艺术，文学  - 嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And music and art and literature.  - Hm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}为了做一个十全十美的漂亮妻子{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So that one day you'd make\na perfectly charming wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是啊，谁都想这样\n有什么不好吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, that was the general idea.\nAnything wrong with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不不不，没什么不好  - 我真是这么想的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No, no, there's nothing wrong with it.  - That's what I thought.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以人人都有一番经历{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, that sort of\nbrings us up-to-date.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如今我的生活是一本打开的书{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now my life\nis an open book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那只是其中的一页{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's only one page.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，是仅有的一页{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, that's the only page.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}对不起，打扰您了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I beg your pardon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢，非常感谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you.\nThank you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不不，这可不好  - 等一等{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No, no. Bad, bad.  - Wait a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你的相机不错啊，可以看看吗？  - 哦，当然可以{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That's a very interesting camera.\nMay I see that?  - Oh, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}还是新的？谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's new, isn't it?\nThank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，别扔，别扔啊！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, please!\nPlease stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这太不幸了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's unfortunate, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这未免太过分了吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That was not\nvery nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你不该那么做  - 是不该{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You shouldn't have done that.  - I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可以一旦登出去\n显然对你对我都不好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, it's obviously no good,\neither of us being seen together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}无论对错人们都会议论\n所以你我还是再见为好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Right or wrong, people will talk,\nand so I guess it had better be good-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这可太遗憾了  - 再见{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That seems a pity.  - Good-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃，怎么回事？你害怕了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, what's the matter?\nAre you afraid?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 怕你？  - 对{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Of you?  - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不是{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你想想我们在船上还得呆上好几天\n这寂寞我怎么能受得了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We have several days to go on this voyage,\nand I can't stand monotony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}晴天时你可以在甲板上长长地散步{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, you can always\ntake long walks in the sunshine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那下雨天我怎么办？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What'll I do if it rains?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不不，我们这样不好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No. No, it's no good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 尤其是对你自己不好吧  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You mean, it's particularly no good for you.  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}和你在一起可是新闻…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Being seen with you\nis news...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我不想让我的形象出现在报纸上{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and I don't want to get\nmy picture in the papers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以，我走我的路…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So, I'll go my way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你呢，走你自己的路{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and you'll go yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}救命！救命！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Help! Help!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！噢，别急，我来了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Oh, here. Let me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，天哪，你可真沉啊  - 怎么了？碰上麻烦了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, my Lord, he's heavy.  - What's the matter? Are you in trouble?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，帮帮忙好吗，他太沉了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Give me a hand.\nHe's a bit heavy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}来，老第，扶好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Come on, chum.\nI've got him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 好了，放开手  - 把腿放下来，让他坐一会儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That's right. No, let go.  - Try it the other way around, Dad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，谢谢，你提醒得很对{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, thank you.\nYou're a great help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你怎么会躺在这儿呢？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, how'd you come\nto do that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我被夹住了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I got...\nI got tangled up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯，下不来了是吗？  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mm-hmm. Couldn't get down, huh?  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嚯，你可真是个人物啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, you're quite a fella.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你也是个人物  - 是吗？为什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You're quite a fella yourself.  - Yes? Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}船上的每一个人都在说你呢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Everybody on the ship's\ntalkin' about ya.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 是吗，都说了些什么？  - 说的什么我不知道…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No kidding? What are they saying?  - I don't know...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}每次他们说的时候就把我赶出来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}on account of every time they start talkin'\nabout ya, they make me leave the room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我也不知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't get it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你来吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You take over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你可得小心点儿，不然会受伤的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You want to watch it, chum.\nYou might hurt yourself.{\r}
