Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我把那张桌子换成单人的了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I changed my table\nto a table for one.{\r}
