Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}昨天我们还在一起共进晚餐？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}after that delightful dinner\nwe had together last night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你会讲盖尔语吗？  - 很流利{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And do you speak Gaelic?  - Fluently.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}“我们走吧”这句话怎么说？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}How do you say,\n"Let's get out of here"?{\r}
