Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，这事儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, well, well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}真有意思？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's good, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这才叫做自欺欺人呢  - 嗯？你说什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- This is what's known as fooling the world.  - Hmm? What did you say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说这才叫做自欺欺人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I said, this is what's known\nas fooling the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我听不清楚你的话，你大声点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I can't hear what you said.\nWhat are you saying?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}得了，你这是想瞒谁呀？\n人人都在盯着我们{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Who do you think you're hiding from?\nEverybody's staring at us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 太可怕了，我可要走了  - 不不，这可太让我伤心了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- This is awful. I'm going to leave.  - No, no. Let me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不要走，我马上就…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Don't worry. That made it worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}快坐下，快坐下{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Sit down! Sit down!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你忘了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You forgot...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 对不起，先生，这是那位小姐的  - 知道，我是想…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Pardon me, sir. That's the lady's purse.  - Yes. I was just...{\r}
