Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}什么…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！噢，天哪，游泳池太小了是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Oh, my, it's\na small pool, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 别打岔好不好，你拿走了我的香烟盒  - 不过这会儿不在手上{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Now, don't change the subject. You've got my cigarette case.\n- Well, not on me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}船要在这儿停五个小时\n这是弗兰契别墅{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We've got a five-hour stopover here.\nWe're coming into Villefranche.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你要上岸吗？  - 是的，去拜访一位女士{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You going ashore?  - Yes. I'm calling on a lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，一站一个？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ah. In every port, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这女士是我的外婆{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}This happens to be\nmy grandmother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 怎么你不相信？  - 嗯，不信{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, don't you believe me?  - Mmm, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你愿意见见她吗？  - 可以，我很想见见你的外婆{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Would you like to meet her?  - Yes, I'd like to meet your grandmother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那咱们就说定了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, you've got a date.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 没想到吧？  - 有点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Surprised?  - All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这就是给你那位外婆的礼物？  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Is this a present for\nyour little old grandmother?  - Yes. Yes, it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 下面可真美  - 啊？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Isn't it beautiful down there?  - Huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我说下面可真美  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I said, isn't it beautiful down there?  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 想不想听句古老的笑话？  - 说吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- But do you want to hear an old joke?  - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 如果下边景色那么美，那么为什么…  - 带我到上边？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- If it's so beautiful down there, why did...  - You bring me up here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不过是句笑话{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's an old joke, all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你的那位外婆真的不是个笑话吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You're quite sure your grandmother\nisn't an old joke?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.36,0:24:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，但愿你能相信我{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I do wish\nyou'd trust me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.29,0:25:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！这地方可真幽静啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! What a divine place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.13,0:25:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}啊！简直绝了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's perfect!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.20,0:25:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我开始相信你有个外婆了  - 哦，这可是新闻{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm beginning to think\nyou have a grandmother.  - Oh, that's surprising.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.97,0:25:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我要找到她给你瞧瞧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll try to find her and prove it.{\r}
