Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}雁努？雁努？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Janou? Janou?{\r}
