Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她一定是去教堂了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She must be in the chapel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}啊，菲德尔！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ah, Fidel!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你好吗，伙计？\n对，是我，你怎么样，小伙子？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}How are you, fella?\nYes, yes, yes. How are you, boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.28,0:25:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这地方可真有特色{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What is it about this place?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.11,0:26:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}周围的一切让人不敢大声说话{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}There's something about it\nthat makes you want to whisper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.82,0:26:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这里宁静极了，就像另一个世界{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's so peaceful here.\nIt's like another world.{\r}
