Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.33,0:26:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}讲讲你的外婆好吗{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Do tell me\nmore about her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.66,0:26:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我外公生前在外交界任职{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}My grandfather was\nin the diplomatic service.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.06,0:26:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}夫妇两个走遍了全世界\n外公离职以后，就来这儿定居{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}They traveled all over the world,\nand when he retired, they came here to live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.07,0:26:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他就埋在教堂后面{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He's buried there\nbehind the chapel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.90,0:26:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}外婆一直守在这儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She stayed on\nto be near him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.34,0:26:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她好像等得…\n等得有点儿不耐烦了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She must be waiting...\nI think a little impatiently...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.84,0:26:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}想早点儿与外公相会{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}For the day\nshe would join him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.92,0:26:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，尼古拉！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nicolo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.93,0:26:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.94,0:26:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，尼古拉！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nicolo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.11,0:26:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你怎么不事先说一声{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}[French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.34,0:26:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我想给您来个大吃一惊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}[French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.61,0:27:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我听说你要结婚了  - 是的，好像是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.48,0:27:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您真是越来越年轻了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}[Ferrante Speaking French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.06,0:27:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，你来可太好了，尼古拉，太好了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nicolo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.50,0:27:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 是她吗？  - 不，不是{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - Non, non.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.14,0:27:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 亲爱的，这位是特瑞·麦凯  - 你好啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Darling, this is Terry McKay.  - How do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.58,0:27:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 您好  - 外婆把你当成我的未婚妻了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- How do you do?  - Janou thought you were\nthe girl I'm going to marry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.48,0:27:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦！  - 真漂亮，我非常喜欢她{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh!  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.88,0:27:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，对不起，我说我非常喜欢你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, pardon moi.\nI was only saying I like you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.59,0:27:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，谢谢，我很高兴{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, thank you. I'm glad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.86,0:27:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请别见怪，我得坐一会儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, if you will excuse me,\nI must sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我祈祷的时间加长了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I am longer\nat my prayers nowadays.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.03,0:27:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，我的膝盖呀！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, my knees!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.60,0:27:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}一把老骨头了啰{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}They're as old as I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.70,0:28:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，我从没见过这么美的地方{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, you have\nthe most beautiful place here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.87,0:28:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 谢谢  - 我真想永远在这儿住下去{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Thank you.  - I think I could stay here forever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，这可不行\n你还太年轻，亲爱的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, no, no.\nYou are too young for that, my dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这里只适合静静地回忆往事…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It is a good place\nto sit and remember...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}而你，你的记忆还没有填满呢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}but you have still\nto create your memories.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.49,0:28:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}还有教堂也这么迷人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And the chapel\nseems so charming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.43,0:28:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，想进去看看吗？  - 哦，可以吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, would you like to go in?  - Oh, may I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.56,0:28:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 当然可以  - 哦，谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - Oh, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，尼古拉！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nicolo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.71,0:28:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你呢，尼古拉…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And you, Nicolo...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.94,0:28:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你有多久没有进教堂了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}how long is it since you\nhave been in a chapel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.11,0:28:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦，这个…  - 还是小时候进的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, well, I...  - Not since you were an altar boy, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 是的  - 去吧，他不会伤害你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Ah, no.  - Go in. It won't hurt you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.25,0:28:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 好吧  - 我去沏壶茶{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- All right.  - I will prepare the tea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.25,0:28:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那么我来帮您  - 不用，不用，去吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Let me help you.  - No, no, no, no. [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.70,0:30:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}马瑞阿斯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Marius!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.49,0:30:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 马瑞阿斯  - 来了，夫人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Marius!  - Oui, madame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.10,0:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，快猜猜谁来了  - 是谁来了？夫人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.58,0:30:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你看呐{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}[French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.91,0:30:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！尼古拉先生！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Monsieur Nicholas!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.28,0:31:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗨！啊！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Ah!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.09,0:31:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 马瑞阿斯！  - 太好了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Marius!  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.46,0:31:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我们又见面了，我太高兴了！太高兴了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}[French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.17,0:31:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 又有孩子了？  - 哦，对的，跟外婆在一起，去看看吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.43,0:31:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这是玛丽  - 喔，你好！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- This is Marie.  - Well, hello!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.20,0:31:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这个是最小的  - 对，她是最小的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.30,0:31:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 一共几个了？  - 哦，七个 你走的时候是…呃，是三个{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.51,0:31:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这是我的朋友马瑞阿斯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}This is my friend Marius.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.61,0:31:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦，您好，小姐  - 您好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, madame.  - Hello.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.61,0:31:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我上次见他时他才三个孩子{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Marius has had three children\nsince I last saw him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.25,0:31:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}马瑞阿斯说法兰西缺人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Marius says\nFrance needs men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以就生了七个女儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So he has seven daughters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.39,0:31:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 去看看我的全家吧  - 去吧，去吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Come to see the rest of my family.  - Yes, go along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.96,0:31:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 可以吗？  - 我顺便和麦凯小姐谈谈{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Sure?  - I should like a little\ntete-a-tete with Miss McKay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.26,0:31:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，雁努，千万客气点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Janou, please be kind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.36,0:31:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不会说你坏话{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I won't betray you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.17,0:31:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我来帮您吧？  - 哦，谢谢，亲爱的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Can I help you?  - Oh, thank you, my dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.04,0:31:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}现在的年轻人对家务一窍不通…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I am glad you are not\nlike so many young people nowadays...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.31,0:32:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你不这样我很高兴{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Above a little housework.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.01,0:32:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我们家兄弟姐妹十个\n人人都得干活…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}There were ten of us in our family.\nWe all had to do our share...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.98,0:32:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不然就不给晚饭吃{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}or go to bed\nwithout supper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.45,0:32:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，这客厅真漂亮！  - 哦，是啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, what a magnificent room!  - Oh, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.29,0:32:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我丈夫曾经是个有名的收藏家{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}My husband was\na great collector.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.46,0:32:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他喜欢漂亮的东西{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He loved\nbeautiful things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.79,0:32:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我也是{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Me too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.79,0:32:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我请过两位管家，可都比我先死了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I should have a housekeeper,\nbut I have outlived two...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.93,0:32:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我太老了，没气力再训练新的了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and I'm too old to start\nbreaking in another one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.70,0:32:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再说我不想瞒你…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Besides, I... I don't\nmind telling you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.80,0:32:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我原来只想活到80岁{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I had planned only\nto live till I was 80.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.64,0:32:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可现在都82了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now I am 82.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.64,0:32:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果一时半会儿死不了\n我得为自己的晚年存点儿钱才行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, if I'm not going to die,\nI must start saving money for my old age.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.68,0:32:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您想得很对{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You're very wise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.82,0:32:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 啊！  - 喜欢吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Ah!  - You like it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.99,0:32:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}喜欢，很美{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mmm, yes.\nIt's charming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.32,0:32:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谁…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Who...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.93,0:32:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 弗伦迪？  - 尼古拉！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Ferrante?  - Nicolo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.39,0:32:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 尼基？  - 是的，他很久以前画的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Nickie?  - Yes. He did that a long time ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.90,0:32:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，他画得还真不错{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, but it's very good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.40,0:32:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他很有点儿才气{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He is very talented.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.90,0:33:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，对不起，我以前一点儿也不知道他会画画{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, forgive me.\nYou see, I had no means of knowing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.81,0:33:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，令人非常惋惜的是他又非常苛刻{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh. Unfortunately,\nhe is also very critical.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.21,0:33:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}才气让他创作\n苛刻让他销毁{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The artist in him would create.\nThe critic would destroy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 到头来他这人一无所成  - 太可惜了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- As a result, he has done nothing since.  - What a pity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.79,0:33:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯，再说，他一直在忙于人们所说的生活{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm-hmm. Besides, he's been too busy...\nliving, as they call it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.62,0:33:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.22,0:33:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我来吧？  - 哦，谢谢，亲爱的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- May I?  - Oh, thank you, my dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.56,0:33:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}给{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}There.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.37,0:33:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，你们到这里来看我真让我兴奋不已{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, it has been such\na tremendous excitement for me, this visit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.87,0:33:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我激动得难以平静{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I am trying\nto appear calm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.77,0:33:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你觉得我现在怎么样？  - 看起来您的气色好极了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Don't you think I do pretty well?  - You do wonderfully well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.58,0:33:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 您请  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Here we are.  - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.85,0:33:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我非常喜欢尼古拉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I love Nicolo so much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.89,0:33:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他还很小的时候…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}When he was a small boy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.22,0:33:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}就弹得一手好钢琴 我们都很惊讶{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}he charmed us all\nwith his piano playing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.39,0:33:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}后来又开始画画{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Then he studied painting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.73,0:34:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}最要命的就是他什么都拿得起来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And the worst of it is\nhe's so good at everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.57,0:34:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不折不扣的万事通{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ajack-of-all-talents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.67,0:34:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}什么事对他都太容易了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Everything comes\ntoo easily to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.34,0:34:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他的注意力总是转向他不会的画法{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He's always attracted by the art\nhe isn't practicing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他没去过的地方，他不认识的女孩儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The place he hasn't been,\nthe girl he hasn't met.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.41,0:34:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}也许我不该和他相识{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Perhaps I shouldn't\nhave met him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.35,0:34:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，亲爱的，你是个例外{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, my dear.\nYou are different.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.92,0:34:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我不妨对你直言不讳…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't mind\nconfessing to you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.76,0:34:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我一直在为他担心{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I have been worried\nabout him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.86,0:34:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 有时候还很害怕  - 为什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Sometimes I'm frightened.  - Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.50,0:34:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我怕生活会赠给尼古拉一张帐单…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That life will present\na bill to Nicolo one day...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.07,0:34:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}而他却无法支付{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and he will find it\nhard to pay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.74,0:34:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我看见你和他在一起，我放心多了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But when I see you with him,\nI feel better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 真的？真的放心？  - 当然是真的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Me? You do?  - Yes. You.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.56,0:35:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}但愿我也能有您这种信心{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I wish I could share\nyour confidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.56,0:35:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}必要时你会有的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You will have it\nwhen you need it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.00,0:35:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这是你的性格{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That is your character.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，一个好妻子能把尼古拉的…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, there is nothing wrong\nwith Nicolo...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.04,0:35:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所有缺点都纠正过来的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}that a good woman\ncouldn't make right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.24,0:35:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.55,0:35:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗨，马瑞阿斯的全家我都见了，七个女儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I saw Marius's entire family.\nSeven daughters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.55,0:35:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我向他贺了喜还和他太太聊了天{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I congratulated him\nand had a nice talk with his wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.22,0:35:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你应该和他再聊一会儿\n别坐了我的帽子{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You should have had a nice talk with him.\nAnd don't sit on my hat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.46,0:35:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}告诉我，你们刚才都聊了些什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Tell me, what have you two\nbeen talking about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.56,0:35:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯，是你想不到的  - 这我相信{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Hmm. Oh, you'd be surprised.  - I'll bet I would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.90,0:35:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我还敢打赌都是外婆一个人在说  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And I'll bet thatJanou did all the talking.  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}外婆告诉我说你小时候很调皮\n一碰上不顺心的事…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She's been telling me that when you were\na little boy and didn't get your own way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}就躺在地板上乱踢乱闹{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}you'd lie on the floor and kick\nand get red in the face.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.74,0:35:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是吗？嗯… 那只眼怎么不挤一下？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Really? Uh... You should've winked the other eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.15,0:35:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢！ - 你怎么说的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh!  - And what did you say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.08,0:36:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说你现在不调皮了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I said you didn't\ndo that anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.38,0:36:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不了！  - 不了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No!  - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.29,0:36:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}现在碰上不顺心的事\n只有自我苦恼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now when you don't get your own way,\nyou just get embarrassed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.26,0:36:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}喝茶吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Want some tea?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.43,0:36:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这件事我不想跟您做出解释{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Remind me not to explain\nthat to you later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.03,0:36:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}好的，我喝杯茶{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, I want some tea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.94,0:36:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 雁努，我给您带了礼物！  - 噢！尼古拉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Janou, I have a gift for you.  - Oh! Nicolo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.84,0:36:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 来瞧瞧  - 还给老太婆带礼物{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Come and see it.  - I am too old for gifts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.31,0:36:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}送礼物可不分老少{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No one's too old for gifts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.65,0:36:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你真不该这么胡乱花钱{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You shouldn't spend\nyour money so recklessly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.75,0:36:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我没花多少，我帮您打开{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It didn't cost much.\nLet me help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.49,0:36:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，尼古拉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nicolo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.87,0:36:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你怎么画的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}How did you do it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.10,0:36:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}根据记忆画的，谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I did it from memory.\nThank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.21,0:36:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦  - 是安德烈…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh.  - It is Andre...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.14,0:37:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我的丈夫{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}my husband.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.55,0:37:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，真像他…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, it's so real...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.91,0:37:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}太像他了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}so like him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.98,0:37:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这张脸真动人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What a remarkable face.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.35,0:37:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你真的是根据记忆画的？  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Did you do that from memory?  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.59,0:37:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}喜欢吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Do you like it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.69,0:37:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，喜欢极了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, it's wonderful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.49,0:37:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}其实我早就画好了\n可我当时不敢把它送给您{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I painted that a long time ago,\nbut I hesitated about giving it to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.44,0:37:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说过他很有才华{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I told you he has talent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.51,0:37:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.82,0:37:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 请，给你的  - 给我的？谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, now, for you.  - For me? Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}给您{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}For you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.19,0:37:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.36,0:37:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}For me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 每人一杯  - 我想说几句祝酒词{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, now.  - I should like to propose a little toast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.60,0:37:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可不知怎么说才好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Uh... I don't quite know\nhow to phrase it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.07,0:37:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您是不是想祝贺他…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, uh, would it\nhave something to do...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.90,0:38:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}婚姻美满幸福快乐？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}with his\nhappy marriage?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.87,0:38:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯，我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm, I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.31,0:38:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这么说吧…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Shall we say...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}祝你们二位的归途顺利愉快{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}may your voyage home\nbe a pleasant one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.42,0:38:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.51,0:38:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不早了，我们得回船上去了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, now, I'm afraid\nwe must be leaving soon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}今天过得真快活{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It has been a good day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我们走之前\n您给我们弹段钢琴好吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now, before we go,\nyou must play the piano for us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.19,0:38:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，不行，尼古拉  - 来吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, no, Nicolo.  - Come along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.52,0:38:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不行，多年没弹了  - 弹一段吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No, no, no.  - Please do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 瞧我这双手  - 没关系，弹吧，弹吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Look at my hands.  - No excuses. Come along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.16,0:38:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}弹吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.13,0:39:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ohh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.00,0:39:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}外婆是个专业钢琴家{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Janou was a concert pianist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.34,0:39:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}过去是{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.84,0:39:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}别忘了是你们强迫我弹的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Remember, I was asked\nto do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.82,0:42:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我真恨开船的汽笛声{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't like boat whistles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.80,0:42:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}亲爱的，外面有风，您披上这个吧？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Don't you think you should put this\naround your shoulders?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.27,0:42:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢，亲爱的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you, my dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.81,0:42:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 披肩真漂亮！  - 喜欢吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It's lovely, isn't it?  - You like it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.38,0:42:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}非常喜欢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.70,0:42:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 将来我会送给你的  - 噢，这哪行啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- One day, I will send it to you.  - Oh, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.35,0:42:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我很愿意送给你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I would like to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.27,0:42:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我就送到这儿了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}This is as far as I go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.27,0:43:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这儿是我居住的小世界的边界{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}This is the boundary\nof my small world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.31,0:43:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.64,0:43:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}啊！一个理想的世界{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! It's a perfect world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.22,0:43:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢您让我闯了进来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you for\nletting me trespass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.55,0:43:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.36,0:43:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}保佑你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Bless you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.39,0:43:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那好，再见了，亲爱的外婆{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, au revoir, dearJanou.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.93,0:43:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我会很快再来看您\n我会经常写信的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll come back to see you very soon,\nand I'll write often.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.10,0:43:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 一定写  - 一定写{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Please do.  - I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.81,0:43:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！祝您愉快，亲爱的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Happy thoughts, darling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.91,0:43:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见，我的孩子{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Adieu, mon petit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.83,0:44:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.07,0:44:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.10,0:44:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.70,0:44:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我到处在找你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I've been looking\neverywhere for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.26,0:44:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}还打了电话给你…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I called your cabin...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.37,0:44:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你哭过了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You've been crying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.77,0:44:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.91,0:44:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是美景把我感动了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Beauty does that to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.48,0:44:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}尼基，谢谢你带我度过了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Nickie, I... I want\nto thank you for the...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.65,0:44:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我一生当中最快活最难忘的一天{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The loveliest and the most memorable day\nI've ever known.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.09,0:44:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你对我外婆真是太好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You were very sweet\nto my little grandmother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.92,0:45:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我准备给她写信{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm going to write to her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.16,0:45:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那太好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That'll be nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.53,0:45:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}散散步吧，嗯？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Let's walk, hmm?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.72,0:46:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}怎么又哭了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No more tears.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.02,0:46:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说了我是被美景感动了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I told you that's what beauty does to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.27,0:46:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}船已驶向大海了，尼基{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We're heading into\na rough sea, Nickie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.64,0:46:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}知道，我们今天改变了航向{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I know. We changed\nour course today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.05,0:46:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯  - 送你回卧舱好吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mm-hmm.  - Shall I see you to your cabin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.62,0:46:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不必送{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.19,0:46:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}晚安{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.49,0:46:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}晚安{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.06,0:47:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请等一下{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Just a moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.80,0:47:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 特瑞…  - 噢！你怎么敢来这儿？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Terry...  - Oh! Why did you come here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.56,0:47:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你知道这很危险  - 亲爱的，我们得好好谈谈{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You know it's dangerous.  - Darling, we got a lot to talk about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.47,0:47:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是该谈谈，可让别人看见\n你知道，对我们两个人都没好处{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I am aware of that, but to be seen together\ncould be disastrous for us both.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.87,0:47:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可是我们得商量一下\n有个问题急需要解决{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I know, but we have some fast thinking to do.\nWe've created a problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.34,0:47:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这我知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.14,0:47:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那么就别让问题复杂化了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So let's not\ncomplicate it any more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.88,0:47:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}作为女人我生来就比你谨慎…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Being a woman,\nI'm naturally more cautious...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.38,0:47:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你不在，我的头脑会更清晰一些{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and I can think more clearly\nwhen you're not around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.72,0:47:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以你回屋想你的\n我就在这儿想我的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So you go think in your room,\nand I'll think in mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.66,0:47:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 好吧  - 在思考中彼此想念{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- All right.  - While we miss each other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.56,0:47:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，这话说得好，说得太好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, that was very sweet,\nwhat you just said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.28,0:48:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 早上好，先生  - 早上好，小姐{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [Irish Accent] Top of the mornin' to you.  - And the rest of the day to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.72,0:48:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 听我说  - 不，不行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No, listen. What?  - No, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.75,0:48:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你快走你的  - 哦，真倒霉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Keep moving.  - Oh, dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.16,0:48:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}等等，先别走{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Wait a minute.\nDon't go away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.46,0:48:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你考虑出什么结果了没有？  - 没有，你快走吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Now, have you come to any conclusions yet?  - No. Keep moving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.36,0:48:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，糟糕{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.63,0:48:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我想你  - 我也想你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I miss you.  - I miss you too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.13,0:48:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那就多给我打电话？  - 我试试吧，不过你知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Why don't you telephone more often?  - I'll try, but you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.34,0:48:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你有话要说吗？  - 没有，我没什么要说的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Were you going to say something?  - I wasn't going to say anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.21,0:48:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}听着，一起吃顿饭总可以吧…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Listen. Couldn't we\nat least eat together...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.21,0:48:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}在你的房间或我的房间？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}in your room or my room?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.55,0:48:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不行，不等我们吃上色拉\n就会被传得满船风雨{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The news would be all around the ship\nbefore we'd had our salad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.98,0:48:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}船员也会说三道四的\n你快朝那边转吧，我头都晕了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The crew talks too. Do go around\nthe other way. You're making me dizzy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.92,0:48:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可以，这样对我也有好处{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Be better for me also,\nI can tell you that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.26,0:48:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，等一等，亲爱的…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, wait a minute.\nDarling. Uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.59,0:48:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}听着，亲爱的，我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Listen, darling, I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.23,0:49:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}真奇怪{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's odd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.03,0:49:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.57,0:49:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 晚上好，先生  - 晚上好，麦凯小姐在吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Good evening, sir.  - Good evening. Is Miss McKay dining?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.41,0:49:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}在，要去找她吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, sir.\nWould you care to join her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.64,0:49:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 她可能喜欢一个人用餐  - 她马上就用完{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I think she prefers to dine alone.  - She's almost finished, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.98,0:49:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哇，嗯…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Whew. Mm, mm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.35,0:49:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}点浓味鱼肉汤，味道好极了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Order the bouillabaisse.\nIt's superb.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.39,0:49:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 非常感谢  - 没什么{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.19,0:49:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，住嘴{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, shut up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.51,0:49:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请进{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Come in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.98,0:49:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你好啊  - 哦，你好啊，哈瑟维先生{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Hello there.  - Oh, hello, Mr. Hathaway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.15,0:49:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}麦凯小姐，弗伦迪在哪儿？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Miss McKay, uh...\nwhere's Ferrante?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.65,0:49:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}弗伦… 噢，我怎么知道？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ferra... Well,\nhow should I know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.72,0:50:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，别装了，有人告诉我他在您这儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, come now. A little bird told me\nhe might be in here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.12,0:50:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，哈瑟维先生\n你不觉得你这样有点儿太无礼了吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, really, Mr. Hathaway.\nDon't you think you're being\na little rude and presumptuous?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.06,0:50:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我根本没看见弗伦迪先生…  - 你好，特瑞{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I haven't seen Mr. Ferrante since...  - Hello, Terry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.90,0:50:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢 呵{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh ho!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.00,0:50:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我想你可能喜欢这本书  - 我看过了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It occurred to me you might like this book.  - Yeah. I've read it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.90,0:50:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}好几天没看见你了\n我还以为你已经下船了呢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I haven't seen you for days.\nI thought you must have got off somewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.74,0:50:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哪儿能呢，这船还没到站呢！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Why, no. We haven't docked anywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.51,0:50:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}也许再也见不着了吧\n麦凯小姐，祝你愉快{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, in case I don't see you again,\nMiss McKay, uh, happy landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.25,0:50:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢，弗伦迪先生\n你别说得这么绝对，也许…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you, Mr. Ferrante,\nand don't think it hasn't been absolute...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.76,0:50:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢 请您先别走\n我想请二位帮个忙可以吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now, slow down. I'm wondering\nif you two would do me a big favor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.03,0:50:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 什么事？  - 能否请你在这照片上签个名字？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- What's that?  - Would you be so kind as to autograph these?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.14,0:50:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我太太，我妹妹和我每人买了一张{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}My wife and my sister and I\neach bought a different one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.11,0:50:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你们买的？  - 哪儿买的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You bought them?  - From whom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.31,0:50:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}从船上的摄影师那儿\n他在上层甲板上摆了一大排{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The ship's photographer.\nHe has a big display up on the promenade deck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.75,0:50:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}正在那儿大力推销呢！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He's doing a wholesale business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.68,0:51:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这样吧，哈瑟维先生，我们先商量一下\n我到哪儿去找你？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, we'll have to think about it.\nNow, where could I find you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.42,0:51:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我嘛，如果不在酒吧的话…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I'll either be\nin the cocktail lounge...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.29,0:51:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}当然就在餐厅里了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}or, of course, the dining room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.36,0:51:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那好吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.13,0:51:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 瞧瞧！  - 噢！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well.  - Oh!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.13,0:51:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我倒不在乎这张，蛮不错的  - 噢，别开玩笑了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I don't mind that one. That's pretty good.  - Oh, do be serious!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.64,0:51:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这太可怕了！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}This is dreadful!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.54,0:51:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我们想尽了办法 还以为瞒住他们呢  - 是啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And after all the pains\nwe took deceiving everybody.  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.21,0:51:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我尤其为你感到遗憾{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm particularly sorry for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.58,0:51:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不过我并不像我预料的那么遗憾{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, I'm not as sorry\nas I thought I'd be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.05,0:51:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}像逃犯一样\n躲来躲去太傻了，不是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It was rather silly,\nhiding like fugitives, wasn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.46,0:51:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，是的，是这样{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Yes, I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.16,0:51:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那么就把这作为新的开端\n去抛头露面怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So, to coin a new cliche,\nshall we join the others?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.43,0:51:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那好吧，干吗不去？\n有什么可顾虑的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, all right. Well, why not?\nWhat have we got to lose?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.83,0:51:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 最后一晚了应该尽情享受  - 对呀{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- The last night. Let's make the most of it.  - Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.55,0:52:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗨，哈瑟维{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hi, Hathaway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.48,0:52:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嘿！再帮个忙吧，咱们换换舞伴{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hey! Do me another favor.\nLet's swap partners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.99,0:52:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 最后一晚上人人都换  - 那太好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It's the last night out. Everybody does it.  - They do? How nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.22,0:52:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}既然这样，我们就来个例外{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}In your case,\nwe'll make an exception.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.40,0:52:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那家伙真怪{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't get that guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.40,0:52:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}♪ 一天又一天 我们久别胜新婚 ♪{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}# Day by day I'm growing fonder #{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.07,0:52:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}♪ 你对我的温柔 ♪{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}# Of those tender things you do #{\r}
