Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.62,0:58:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 尼基  - 噢，我担心极了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Nickie.  - Oh, I was so worried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.12,0:58:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我连外套都没来得及穿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I didn't even have time\nto get dressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.32,0:58:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}凌晨五点我才睡着{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I didn't get\nto sleep until 5:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.32,0:58:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我根本就没睡  - 哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I didn't sleep at all.  - Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.49,0:58:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 好，你仔细听着  - 说吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Now, listen carefully.  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.56,0:58:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果一切顺利的话\n我是指你我两个人六个月以后…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}If everything goes right,\nand I mean for both of us, in six months...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.83,0:58:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 给，我都写在这纸上了  - 现在能看吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Here. I started to write it out.  - Should I read it now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.40,0:58:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯哼  - 好吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mm-hmm.  - All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.44,0:58:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 亲爱的，是指我？  - 嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- "Darling..." that's me?  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.47,0:59:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我答应与你相见\n七月一号下午五点{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"You have a date, my beloved,\nJuly 1 at 5:00."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.94,0:59:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 怎么没写地址  - 地点随你 哪儿都行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- But you don't say where.  - You name the place, and I'll obey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.91,0:59:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}定哪儿呢，脑子都乱了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't know.\nI can't think.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.91,0:59:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}帝国大厦顶层你看怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}How about the top of\nthe Empire State Building?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.95,0:59:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，太好了，再合适不过了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, yes, that's perfect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.59,0:59:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那是纽约离上帝最近的地方  - 那好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It's the nearest thing to heave we have in New York.  - Well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.42,0:59:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}第102层，别忘了乘电梯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The 102nd floor,\nand don't forget to take the elevator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.12,0:59:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我才不乘呢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, I won't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.23,0:59:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}亲爱的，万一事情不顺利…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Darling, if things\ndon't work out...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.63,0:59:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}别这样说，我不要听{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Don't talk like that.\nI'm not listening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.33,0:59:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 万一有一方不能赴约…  - 我们都会去的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- But just in case one of us is...  - We'll both be there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.27,0:59:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 一定要坚信  - 我坚信{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Hold the thought.  - Hold the thought.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.44,0:59:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 多保重  - 多保重{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Take care.  - Take care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.62,1:00:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.23,1:01:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢！尼基，亲爱的！  - 你好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh! Nickie darling!  - Hello!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.77,1:01:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你能来我太高兴了  - 哦，尼基  - 你好吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, I'm so glad to see you.  - Oh, Nickie.  - How've you been?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.27,1:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}见到你真是太高兴了\n旅途顺利吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm so glad to see you.\nDid you have a good trip?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.78,1:01:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}还不错，不过就是有些颠簸，不过还是很愉快{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Not too bad.\nA little rough in spots, but very pleasant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.25,1:01:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请别动照张相\n好极了，谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hold it for a picture.\nThat's fine. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.15,1:01:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 看见皮基先生了吗？  - 我也来照一张？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Did you get to see Pinky?  - May I have one, too, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.68,1:02:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 可以，这样行吗？  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Yes, how's this?  - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.02,1:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 没有，可能是去了丹吉尔  - 我可以再照一张吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No, I think he's on his way to Tangiers.  - May I have another one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.72,1:02:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他总是东跑西颠的，可以{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He's always going off\nsomeplace. Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.73,1:02:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 太好了，谢谢  - 再来一张{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That's fine. Thank you.  - Another one, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.79,1:02:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，对不起，我有点儿要紧事先过去一下{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, excuse me.\nI have an important appointment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.13,1:02:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 对不起，非常抱歉  - 可以吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Excuse me. Thank you so much.  - May I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.13,1:02:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 特瑞，亲爱的  - 你好，亲爱的，好久没见了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Terry darling.  - Hello, darling. It's been so long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.37,1:02:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}太好了，你终于回来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's wonderful\nto have you back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.74,1:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}回来真好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's wonderful\nto be back, Ken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.94,1:02:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}亲爱的，车在那儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Darling, the car's around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.22,1:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 怎么啦？我们走吧？  - 对对，走吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- What's the matter? Shall we get going?  - Yes, thanks. Shall we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.52,1:02:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 车就停在这儿  - 太好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- The car's right out here.  - Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.80,1:02:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}亲爱的，有件事我得跟你商量一下{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Darling, there's something\nI must discuss with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.97,1:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}咱们在这儿安安静静地单独聊聊…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's been on my mind, so let's go in here\nwhere we can be alone and quiet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.91,1:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他们在这儿干什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What in the world\nis all this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.04,1:02:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我没告诉你吗？  - 没有{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Didn't I mention it?  - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.08,1:03:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}电视台记者一直追着要采访我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Dear, the TV people have been after me\nfor an interview, so I finally said yes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.38,1:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我的条件是给我的慈善机构捐笔款子\n他们果真捐了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}if they give a big donation\nto my favorite charity, and they did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.12,1:03:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你不介意吧，亲爱的？\n这是件好事{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You don't mind, do you, darling?\nIt's for a good cause.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.32,1:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 倒也是 但该事先告诉我一声  - 哦，听我说，我知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I wish you'd let me know.  - Oh, listen, I know you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.52,1:03:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果事先告诉你\n你准会不肯下船了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}If I'd told you,\nI'd never have got you off the ship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.83,1:03:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}一号机负责近距离拍摄{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Camera one,\ntake close-ups.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.23,1:03:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}亲爱的，这是刘易斯先生\n就是他要采访我们{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Nickie, dear, this is Mr. Lewis\nwho's going to interview us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.73,1:03:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 富尔顿·刘易斯先生  - 啊，是罗伯特{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mr. Fulton Q. Lewis.  - Uh, Robert.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.47,1:03:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}罗伯特·富尔顿，您好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Robert Fulton,\nhow do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.47,1:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，是罗伯特·刘易斯\n人们经常弄错{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, Robert Q. Lewis,\nbut everybody does that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.47,1:03:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这样吧，您来晚了，弗伦迪先生{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You're a little late, and we've got to go on the air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.47,1:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 转播马上就要开始了，我们现在开始吧？  - 好的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Would you mind coming over\nhere, Miss Clarke, please?  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.61,1:03:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你们到这边来坐好不好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Sit yourselves right down here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.00,1:03:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}好，你们就坐在这个位置，我就问几个问题…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm going to ask a few questions,\nthen we're going to...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.75,1:03:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他的面部怎么样？\n太亮了？那好，哈里{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What about his face?\nShiny. Look, uh, Harry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.12,1:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}擦一下脸？\n哈里，动做要快一点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Would you mind a little makeup?\nHarry, just blot it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.72,1:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 对不起，亲爱的，一会儿就好  - 但愿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm sorry, darling. It'll be over with soon.  - I hope so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.89,1:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那件…那件白衬衫…\n反差太大？好的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Incidentally, that white shirt...\nHow about that? Glares.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.59,1:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 您有没有蓝色的衬衫？  - 没有，没带{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You don't happen to have a blue shirt?  - No, not with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.36,1:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，好的，没关系，我们有办法{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ah, well, yes.\nWell, look, don't worry. We'll manage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.96,1:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}现在我来解释一下我的打算\n我想问二位几个问题…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Let me explain what I'm going to do.\nI'd like to ask a few questions about how you met...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.13,1:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 就几个  - 好吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Just a few.  - I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.14,1:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你们是怎么认识\n您有什么打算等等问题{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Just how you met, what your plans are\nand things like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.41,1:04:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 放松点儿，不必紧张  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You make yourselves comfortable.  - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.57,1:04:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 还有五秒钟，刘易斯先生  - 知道了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Five seconds, Mr. Lewis.  - Right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.88,1:04:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}还有眼睛就是要看着镜头\n那个红灯一亮就表示开始{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}One thing, watch the camera.\nWhen the red light is on, you're on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.01,1:04:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}瞧，已经亮了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yeah? Well, it's on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.85,1:04:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，观众们好\n欢迎您收看本集《千家万户》节目…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, hello there, and welcome to another\nHouse to House program...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.32,1:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}本节目由本顿婴儿公司提供赞助{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}brought to you by\nthe Benton Baby Food Company.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.26,1:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}别忘了，本顿食品 育儿佳品{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Remember, Benton's\nbuilds better babies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.46,1:04:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}今天我们的摄像机\n架在了洛伊斯·克拉克小姐的府上…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Today, our cameras are placed\nin the home of Miss Lois Clarke...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.17,1:04:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她是美国最富有的女继承人之一{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}heiress to one of\nAmerica's greatest fortunes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.87,1:04:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}一会儿我们将见到克拉克小姐…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}In just a moment,\nwe'll meet Miss Clarke...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.14,1:04:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}和她未婚夫尼基·弗伦迪先生…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and her fiance,\nMr. Nickie Ferrante...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.74,1:04:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我请他们谈谈\n他们真实动人的罗曼史…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and talk to them about their\nwonderful true-to-life romance...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.44,1:04:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他们的爱情故事\n已经登在了全国各大报纸的头版头条…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}which has gotten headlines\nin papers all over the country...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.68,1:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}引起了世界各国的瞩目{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}a romance which has captured\nthe imagination of the whole world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.03,1:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}但首先请看本顿广告…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But first...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.42,1:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您觉得他俩相爱吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Do you think they're in love?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.22,1:04:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我怎么知道，格拉迪斯  - 我一直盼着见见尼基·弗伦迪{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I wouldn't know, Gladys.  - I can't wait to see that Nickie Ferrante.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.73,1:04:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}虽然我不知道采访人会问什么…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't know what the\n$64 million question was...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.93,1:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}但他肯定知道该怎么回答{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}but he's certainly\ngot the answer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.67,1:05:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}倒霉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Point killer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.37,1:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}特瑞，亲爱的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Terry, darling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.45,1:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hmph.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.65,1:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呆会儿我要问问 你的吻怎么不那么温柔了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Remind me to ask you later\nwhy your kisses don't seem quite the same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.19,1:05:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}但愿是因为离别得太久了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Maybe you're just\nout of practice, I hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.29,1:05:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}干吗非得看这破玩意儿？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We don't need\nthat darn thing on, do we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.87,1:05:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，你还没有换衣服{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I see you\nhaven't changed yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.41,1:05:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我给你的时间\n足够换件更漂亮的衣服…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I thought I gave you plenty of time\nto get into something more...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.81,1:05:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是这样，肯，我们要谈的事太多了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, Ken, we have\nso much to talk about...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.38,1:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再说我觉得这件衣服挺不错的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and I can just think better\nin this outfit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.08,1:05:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，亲爱的\n我以为旅行会对你有益处{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, darling,\nI hoped the trip would be good for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.82,1:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可是你的气色不很好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But I'm afraid\nyou don't look so well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.72,1:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}怎么回事？\n是不是太颠簸了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What's the matter?\nWas it a rough crossing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.36,1:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，是的，是有点儿颠簸{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes... Yes.\nYes, it was a little.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.73,1:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.46,1:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说，肯，节目肯定很有趣{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, Ken, that program\nmight have been amusing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.13,1:06:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}洛伊斯·克拉克和\n尼基·弗伦迪马上就要出来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Lois Clarke and Nickie Ferrante\nwere about to come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.07,1:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我只对你感兴趣\n如果你觉得好看…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm only interested in you, dear,\nbut if it'll entertain you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.41,1:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯哼，会好看的  - 那好吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Mm-hmm. Yes, it will.  - Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.22,1:06:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}弗伦迪先生，您的欧洲之行\n一定有不少非凡的经历吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Say, Mr. Ferrante, you must have\nhad some wonderful experiences in Europe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.12,1:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.15,1:06:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那么，能不能请您多谈几句呢？  - 不行{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, would you care to expand that statement?  - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.26,1:06:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.19,1:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我要问的问题实在是太多了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}There are so\nmany questions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.36,1:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，弗伦迪和你在同一条船上是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I forgot Ferrante was on\nthe same boat with you, wasn't he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.17,1:06:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你说的对  - 跟他认识了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Yes, he was.  - Did you meet him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.20,1:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.87,1:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 他潇洒吗？  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Was he charming?  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.04,1:06:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯，我肯定尼基…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I'm sure Nickie has all...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.04,1:06:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他迷人吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Fascinating?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.05,1:06:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 很好，好，噢，噢  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, good, oh, oh.  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.08,1:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 对，我们在这方面没什么危机…  - 不可抗拒吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, you know, financial difficulties often cause...\n- Irresistible?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.92,1:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 婚姻解体…  - 哦，对不起{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- The breakup of marriages...  - Oh, I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.19,1:07:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我敢肯定不会是你的一个…  - 我太多心了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm sure that won't be one of your...  - That wasn't like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.36,1:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我收回刚才的话  - 那不是我们的难题{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I withdraw that remark.  - That won't be one of our difficulties.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.66,1:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那么，请问，弗伦迪先生\n您是不是第一次过伉俪生活呢？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, tell me, Mr. Ferrante, is this\nyour first experience with connubial bliss?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.96,1:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您能不能再说一遍？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Would you mind\nrephrasing the question?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.57,1:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，亲爱的！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, darling!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.57,1:07:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他的意思是问你是不是第一次结婚？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He means is this your\nfirst experience with marriage?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.67,1:07:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦，是这意思  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, that's what he meant. - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.64,1:07:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃，很好，您是否按您太太习惯的…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Uh, good. Do you intend\nto support your wife in the...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.58,1:07:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 方式供养她…  - 是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- uh, manner to which, uh...  - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.68,1:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 真有意思  - 怎么供养？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That's very funny.  - Doing what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.05,1:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我打算…我打算重新开始画画{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I'm... I'm going to begin\nto paint again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.56,1:07:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}靠卖画来供养我妻子{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's how I intend\nto support my wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.59,1:07:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，是吗…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, well...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.16,1:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那你可得多准备点儿…颜料{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's certainly going to take\nan awful lot of... paint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.40,1:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃…我是说你们已经满屋子都是稀世名画了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I mean, you already have\na house full of masterpieces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.14,1:07:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}说得对，再说我没料到\n你会有这样的打算…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, we have, and I didn't realize\nthat you were going to...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.14,1:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 反正我要画画  - 哦，是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm still going to paint.  - Oh, really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.18,1:08:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我是说你不是早就不画了吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I mean, I just thought\nyou'd given all that up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.45,1:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，我不该放弃{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I know,\nbut I shouldn't have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.82,1:08:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 哦，不过我相信尼基一定有其他什么打算  - 我是有{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, I'm sure Nickie has all kinds of plans.  - Yes, I have.{\r}
