Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.17,1:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你画这个没请模特吗？  - 没有，我请不起{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You did this without a model?  - Yeah, I couldn't afford one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.34,1:10:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}怎么啦？\n我的记忆出毛病了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What is it?\nSomething wrong with my memory?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.35,1:10:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我觉得情绪有点儿低落  - 哪里{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It's getting a trifle dim.  - No.{\r}
