Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.38,1:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可你这罗基的笔名一钱不值{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But signing "Rossi"\ndon't mean a thing.{\r}
