Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.01,1:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}新的罗基正在挨饿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and the new Rossi is starving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.78,1:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你想在三个月之内就打响吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}What do you expect\nin three months?{\r}
