Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.44,1:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我想尝尝挣钱的滋味{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I want the thrill\nof earning that first dollar.{\r}
