Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.87,1:18:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，对不起，肯，我恐怕已经晚了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, forgive me, Ken.\nI'm terribly late.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.04,1:18:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 现在几点了？  - 哦，现在是差五分五点{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- What time is it?  - It's, uh, five minutes to 5:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.78,1:18:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢！噢，见到你我太高兴了，肯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh! Oh, it's been good\nseeing you, Ken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.24,1:18:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我也很高兴，特瑞\n要说的话太多了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's good seeing you, too, Terry.\nThere's so much to talk to you about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.85,1:18:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}实在对不起，我有点儿急事{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm sorry,\nbut I'm in such a hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.85,1:18:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我们找地方喝一杯吧？  - 不行，我真的有急事{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Can't we go someplace and have a cocktail?  - I really am in a hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.25,1:18:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我有很多话要说  - 这样吧你可以打个电话…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- But I have so much to say to you.  - Why don't you give me a call...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.09,1:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，不行，不能打，因为我要接…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You can't do that,\nbecause I'm getting marr...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.89,1:18:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 要结婚？  - 是的，我要结婚了，肯，我已经来迟了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You're getting married?  - Yes. Yes, I am, Ken, and I'm very, very late.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.59,1:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你刚才说几点了？  - 哦，差四分五点{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- What time did you say it was?  - Uh, four minutes to 5:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.76,1:18:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 啊，再见了，肯  - 特瑞{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, good-bye, Ken.  - Terry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.03,1:18:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我忠心地希望你能找到幸福…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I really hope\nyou've found happiness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.40,1:18:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}万一你需要帮忙…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and if you're ever\nin need of anything...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.57,1:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}需要有人爱你，尽管跟我打电话{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}like someone to love you,\ndon't hesitate to call me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.44,1:19:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，我不需要，再见了，肯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No. No, I won't.\nGood-bye, Ken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.31,1:19:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见，祝你好运{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good-bye. Good luck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.42,1:19:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我真是急糊涂了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Shows what a state I'm in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.45,1:19:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}以为帝国大厦在那边\n当然是在这边儿！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I thought the Empire State Building\nwas this way, and, of course, it's that way!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.13,1:19:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我就在这儿下车吧，我有点儿急事{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I think I'll get out here,\nbecause I'm in a hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.50,1:19:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 给你，别找钱了  - 急什么呀小姐？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Here you are. Keep the change.  - What's the rush, lady?{\r}
