Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.37,1:21:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}快调转船头！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Turn the boat around!{\r}
