Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.44,1:21:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，尼基，帮我把船头调过来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nickie, help me\nturn the boat around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.41,1:21:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你比我…你比我的劲儿大多了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, you're so...\nYou're so much stronger than I am.{\r}
