Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.45,1:21:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你现在需要安静  - 可我…我需要他！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You must be quiet now.  - But... But I need him!{\r}
