Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.66,1:21:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我…我必须把船调过来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I... I must...\nI must... aah.{\r}
