Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.51,1:22:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她能否走路还很难说{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's hard to say\nif she'll ever walk again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.31,1:22:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}得过很长时间才能知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We won't know\nfor a long while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.51,1:22:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这可…太遗憾了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's... That's bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.45,1:22:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}您大概已经知道 他喊叫的人不是我{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I guess you've gathered by now\nI'm not the man she was screaming about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.45,1:22:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她正准备去结婚{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She was on her way\nto marry him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.79,1:22:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 他知道这消息吗？  - 不{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Does he know of her condition?  - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.30,1:22:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她说 在你们能否确认她康复之前…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She said until you know\nwhat you say you won't know for a while...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.80,1:22:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她不想让他知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}she'd rather he didn't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.40,1:22:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 她是个好姑娘  - 是啊，我有同感{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- She seems nice.  - I... I think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.28,1:22:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她想见你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She wants to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.98,1:23:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}去吧，我一会儿就来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Go ahead.\nI'll be in shortly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.75,1:23:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你好，肯  - 你好，特瑞{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Hello, Ken.  - Hello, Terry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.59,1:23:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我告诉她我不知道她能否活过今天{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I told her I didn't know whether or not\nshe'd be with us today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.16,1:23:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你骗我的，神父{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Fooled you, Father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.06,1:23:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}肯，我把你和我事告诉了神父{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Ken, I told\nFather McGrath about us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.03,1:23:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他答应帮我找个工作，是吗，神父？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He's going to find me a job,\naren't you, Father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.44,1:23:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你还是先把身体养好，特瑞  - 他说得对{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You'd better get well first, Terry.  - He's right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.24,1:23:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 然后我再帮你找工作  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Then I'll try and come up with something.  - Hmm. Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.01,1:23:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 先别着急  - 好吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Take it easy.  - Yes.{\r}
