Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.58,1:26:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 跟您来过的那姑娘  - 谢谢，马瑞阿斯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - Merci, Marius.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.61,1:26:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}先生 您要在这儿住几天吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}[French]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.72,1:27:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我还没定下来  - 哦，那好，先生{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- [French]  - [French]{\r}
