Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.62,1:32:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}对，你这个主意我倒是同意{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, I'm inclined to agree\nwith you about that one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.82,1:32:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 得了，你画这几幅画的时候\n我知道你在想些什么  - 是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I can read your state of mind\nwhen you painted this.  - Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.46,1:32:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你画这幅画的时候心里难过极了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You were very sorry for yourself\nwhen you painted this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.70,1:32:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那张画是我八月份画的，别谈了  - 嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- That one was painted in August. Doesn't count.  - Hmm!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.17,1:32:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}画这张画时心里很气恼\n破碎的心被气愤挫败了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You were angry here.\nYou were getting over your broken heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.70,1:32:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 破碎的心？噢，我的心什么时候破碎过  - 没碎就更好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Broken heart? Oh, that stuff's not for me.  - I'm glad to hear that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.61,1:32:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 还是谈谈这边几幅吧  - 我这就谈{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Come on. Let's get down to this end. Come on.  - I'm coming to that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.98,1:33:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}咱们马上就谈{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm coming to that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.31,1:33:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你瞧，尼基，你成为真正的画家了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yeah, here, Nickie,\nyou became a painter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.99,1:33:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢，我也觉得这幅画画得还可以{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you. I'm not exactly\nashamed of that one myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.82,1:33:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我要说的千言万语全都画在上面了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I had a great deal to say,\nand I painted it instead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.99,1:33:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}长时间地远离家乡\n那种孤独和寂寞给人以启迪，使得你…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Your being away, alone, for a long time,\nhas given you that grasp of...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.63,1:33:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我来接，记住刚才的话茬{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll get it. Remember where you were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.67,1:33:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}一会儿接着说{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I want to hear more of that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.37,1:33:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}喂？我是科尔曼颜料商店{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hello? Courbet's\nPaint and Varnish Store.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.54,1:33:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}尼基？我听说你今天回来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Nickie? I read\nyou arrived today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.71,1:33:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}洛伊斯，是你呀，你怎么知道我在这儿？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Lois, how nice.\nHow did you know I was here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.45,1:33:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我打到你的饭店\n他们说你可能在这儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I called your hotel, and they said\nyou could be reached at this number.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.02,1:33:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，尼基，我天天都在想你\n早上，中午，晚上…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, Nickie, I've been thinking about you\nmorning, noon and night...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.45,1:33:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}时时刻刻都在想{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}and in-between times too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.46,1:33:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我想知道你能不能和我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I was wondering\nif maybe you could...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.46,1:33:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃，恐怕…呃，不行，不行\n这主意倒是不错，我很感激{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Aha. Well... Oh, no, no,\nI like the idea all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.26,1:33:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不过我下午可能没有时间{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's a nice offer, but I don't think\nI can make it this afternoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.10,1:34:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯，要是你来不了的话…\n噢，要是能来该多好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, if you can't do that...\nOh, I wish you would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.54,1:34:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Mmm-mmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.61,1:34:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}非常感谢，谢谢你的盛情邀请{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thanks anyway. Nicest thing\nthat's happened today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.31,1:34:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，那你晚上来看芭蕾好吗{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh. But you could\nmake the show tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.02,1:34:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我把你的票留在售票处{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I'll leave a ticket\nat the box office anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.85,1:34:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}一定来吧\n还有，尼基！{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Do try to make it.\nAnd, Nickie!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.72,1:34:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不管有什么事\n把看完芭蕾以后的时间留给我？呵{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Whatever you do, don't plan anything\nfor after the show, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.72,1:34:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 位子真不错  - 什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I love our seats.  - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.86,1:34:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说我们的位子真不错{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I said I love our seats.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.42,1:35:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这场芭蕾真不错  - 谢谢您的邀请{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- We enjoyed it very much.  - Thank you for asking us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.49,1:35:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，我很愿意，不介意的话\n弗伦迪先生要送我回去了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, it was a pleasure. If you don't mind,\nMr. Ferrante will see me home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.26,1:35:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 那好吧，晚安  - 晚安{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Very well. Good night.  - Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.69,1:35:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 晚安  - 晚安{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Good night.  - Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.17,1:35:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你想去哪儿？  - 你来决定吧，尼基{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Now, where would you like to go?  - Suppose you decide, Nickie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.04,1:35:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}确切地说这是你的晚上{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}After all,\nthis is your evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.04,1:35:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我离开的时间太长了\n不知道现在人们爱去哪儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I've been away so long\nI have no idea where people go nowadays.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.04,1:35:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我的大衣{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}My coat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.45,1:35:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hello.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.62,1:36:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hello.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.84,1:36:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}特瑞，让我告诉他吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Terry, please let me tell him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.34,1:36:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，不，不能{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, no. No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.68,1:36:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我去叫住他  - 不，千万别去，求你了，肯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'll go get him.  - No, please. Please, Ken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.99,1:36:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}真难为你了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's pretty rough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.46,1:36:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}今天是你第一次出来\n可偏偏碰见了他{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The first time you're able to get out,\nand you have to run into him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.29,1:36:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我也只能说一声“你好”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And all I could\nsay was hello.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.34,1:36:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}好了，戏演完了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, the show's over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.27,1:36:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}小伙子得到了姑娘，走吧？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Boy got the girl.\nShall we go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.18,1:36:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}请稍等一下{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll only be a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.48,1:36:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.14,1:37:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}晚安，洛伊斯，谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good night, Lois,\nand thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.24,1:37:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}今天晚上我不应该\n带你去那儿看芭蕾，是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Taking you to a show tonight\nwasn't a very good idea, was it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.54,1:37:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 圣诞快乐，洛伊斯  - 圣诞快乐，尼基，再见{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Merry Christmas, Lois.\n- Merry Christmas, Nickie, and... auf Wiedersehen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.48,1:38:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}唉，别人这时候都出去狂欢…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I think it's terrible\nto have to take you home...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.48,1:38:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你却叫我带你回家\n不太合适吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}just when everyone else\nis going out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.05,1:38:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可…这就是我的生活{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Tsk. C'est la vie,\net cetera.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.19,1:38:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}特瑞，我再问你一遍{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Terry, let me ask you again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.13,1:38:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}为什么不让我来帮助你？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Why won't you\nlet me help you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.33,1:38:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那好吧，我就再回答你一遍{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}All right then,\nI will tell you again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.74,1:38:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果你花钱为我治病，他会不高兴的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now, if you paid for my getting well,\nhe wouldn't like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.44,1:38:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果他不高兴，我也会不高兴{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And if he didn't like it,\nI wouldn't like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.54,1:38:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果你给我治好了\n我跑去找他，你又会不高兴{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Then if you did get me well,\nand I went to him, you wouldn't like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.11,1:38:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}至少应该让他知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But certainly\nhe ought to know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.11,1:38:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，如果他了知道我这样\n他肯定会设法为我付医疗费…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, because if he found out,\nhe'd insist upon doing it himself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.28,1:38:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可他到哪儿去弄钱呢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}if he had the money,\nwhich I doubt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.19,1:38:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}万一我再恢复不了，噢，那可太残酷了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And then if I didn't get well, ooh!\nThat'd be awful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.76,1:38:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不行，当我能走路那天…\n我能跑向他的时候，我再告诉他{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, unless I can walk to him... and when\nI say walk, I mean run... he'll never know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.56,1:38:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我能自理，我有个工作\n又赚了一些钱{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I'm fine.\nI've got my job, and I'm on a budget.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.46,1:38:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果治疗顺利的话\n如果我能完好如初…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}If things come out right,\nand then maybe if I'm a very good girl...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.80,1:39:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}下一个圣诞节我就能如愿了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll get what\nI want next Christmas.{\r}
