Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.08,1:43:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你不舒服吗？  - 没…没有，我感觉很好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- You feeling all right?  - Y-Yes. Yes. I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.29,1:43:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我想休息一会儿  - 那好，那好，那好{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- I'm just resting.  - Good, good. Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.83,1:43:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃…很久没见了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, it's...\nbeen a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.13,1:43:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是啊，很久了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, hasn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.46,1:43:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我太高兴了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, it is good to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.23,1:43:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你刚才说过了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You said that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.30,1:44:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 我可以…  - 哦，可以，请，坐吧{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- May I, uh...  - Oh, yes, please, do. Sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.94,1:44:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我一会儿就走，我想你不会介意{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'll only be a minute.\nI'm sure you don't mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.11,1:44:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不，不，当然不{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, no, of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.68,1:44:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，这儿的环境不错嘛？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, is this\nthe breathtaking view?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.45,1:44:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}就是位置高了一点儿{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, the altitude\nbothered me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.96,1:44:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yeah, yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.63,1:44:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你一定…纳闷我怎么会找到这儿来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I'll, uh, I'll bet\nyou're wondering how I got here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.93,1:44:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，我是很纳闷{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, yes. Yes, yes, I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.90,1:44:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是这样\n我在电话薄上查一个叫麦基伯德的人{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I was, uh, I was looking\nthrough a telephone book\nfor a man named McBride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.57,1:44:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}碰巧我发现了特·麦凯这个名字{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And I, uh, I came across\nthe name T. McKay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.91,1:44:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我对自己说“噢，这会不会是特瑞·麦凯…我的老朋友呢？”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And I said to myself,\n"Oh, now, could that possibly be\nTerry McKay, my old friend?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.02,1:44:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 还真是的  - 真是巧了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And it was.  - Yes, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.22,1:44:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}然后我又对自己说…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And then I said to myself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.42,1:44:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}惭愧呀，我有点儿对不起麦凯小姐{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"Well, now, I haven't been\nvery nice to Miss McKay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.79,1:45:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我记得有一天我跟她约好要见面，可是我，我却没有赴约{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}After all, I had an appointment\nwith her one day, and, uh, I didn't keep it."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.17,1:45:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你没去赴约…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You didn't keep...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.27,1:45:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}没有{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.07,1:45:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}没去 所以我对自己说…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, so I said to myself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.11,1:45:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我现在经常自言自语{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I talk to myself\nquite a lot these days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.35,1:45:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说我那样对待像麦凯小姐\n这样的老朋友太不对了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I said, " Well, that's not a very nice way\nto treat an old friend like Miss McKay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.35,1:45:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我得向麦凯小姐道歉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I must apologize\nto Miss McKay."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.85,1:45:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果一个人失了约\n他理应向对方道歉 对吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Don't you agree when someone doesn't keep\nan appointment they should apologize?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.59,1:45:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}对，噢，很对，我觉得你说得太对了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes. Oh, yes, I think\nyou're absolutely right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.66,1:45:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我…我觉得失约的人…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I-I... Well, I-I think the least\npeople could do is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.23,1:45:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}起码应该向对方说一声对不起什么的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}to say they're...\nsorry or something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.27,1:45:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以我来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So here I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.97,1:45:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你想得真周到{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's very sweet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.04,1:45:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我应该来{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I thought so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.98,1:45:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我经常想起你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I've often wondered about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.48,1:45:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 也惦记你怎么样啦  - 此话当真？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And how you were.  - Did you really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.79,1:45:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}当然是真的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, really.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.96,1:46:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，是啊，我也常想起你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I... I've often\nthought about you too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.96,1:46:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那么，我没有去赴约你没生气吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Then, uh, then you weren't angry\nbecause I wasn't there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.36,1:46:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你当时一定很生气{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I mean, you must\nhave been at first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.83,1:46:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.17,1:46:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我是很气，我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, yes, I was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.74,1:46:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我当时给气坏了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}At first, I was furious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.28,1:46:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我说道：“他怎么能这个样\n竟然来耍弄我？”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I said, " He can't do this to me.\nWho does he think he is?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.25,1:46:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦 你等了多久？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Hmph. How long\ndid you wait?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.51,1:46:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我是说你等了多久？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I mean, did you wait long?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.92,1:46:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}呃，是的，我等了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Uh, well, let's...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.09,1:46:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 等了很久，我等啊\n等啊，一直等到…  - 半夜{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Well, yes. Yes, I... I waited until about...  - Midnight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.32,1:46:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.83,1:46:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}然后你怎么办？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And then what did you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.23,1:46:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我那时简直气疯了 嗯{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, then I got\nreally mad. Mmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.20,1:46:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你可以想象我孤零零地站在…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, you can imagine,\nstanding up there on the...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.00,1:46:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}站在暴风雨里{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, in the thunderstorm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.67,1:46:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}站在暴风雨里{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}In a thunderstorm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.71,1:46:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你那会儿是怎么想的？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Then what did you say\nto yourself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.31,1:47:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我对自己说“算了，回家喝个一醉方休吧”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, then I said,\n"Oh, go on home and get tight."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.82,1:47:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 可你并没有喝醉  - 我没醉？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- But you didn't do that.  - Didn't I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.65,1:47:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}没有…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No. Well, uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.76,1:47:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我看，你可能是…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}maybe just a little one...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.13,1:47:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}每一个小时喝一点儿，喝一个来月{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}every hour\nfor about a month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.70,1:47:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 这能怨我吗？  - 哦，当然不能怨你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Can you blame me?  - Oh, I should say not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.90,1:47:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我起码应该写封信向你道歉{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}The least I could have done\nwas to have sent you a note.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.30,1:47:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}也许等你想起来写的时候\n我已经不知去向了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, perhaps by the time you thought of it,\nyou didn't know where to reach me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.57,1:47:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你答应过我，我们再见面的时候你会问我{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But you swore if you ever\nsaw me again you'd ask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.41,1:47:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不对，不对{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}N-No. N-No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.78,1:47:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我记得当时是说\n如果可能你我都去赴约地点{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I remember we said that if\nwe could make it, we'd be there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.82,1:47:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果一方没有赴约…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And if one of us\ndidn't show up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.35,1:47:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}那一定有充足的理由{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}it would be for\na darn good reason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.49,1:47:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是这么说的吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Did we say that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.79,1:47:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是的，我们确实是这么约定的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, that... that is\nexactly what we said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.43,1:47:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你能详细地说说吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, like what for instance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.43,1:47:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以，既然这样，我不会再向你问什么了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So, there'll be no more\nquestions asked... I hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.80,1:47:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 想抽支烟吗？  - 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Would you like a cigarette?  - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.68,1:48:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}谢谢你，尼基{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Thank you, Nickie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.51,1:48:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这可真有意思？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Isn't that wonderful?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.75,1:48:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我赶到这儿来是为了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I walked all the way\nhere just to...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.19,1:48:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可现在我连你为什么不去都不想问了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And now I'm not even supposed to ask you\nwhy you weren't there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.96,1:48:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你说怪不怪？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Isn't it strange?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.40,1:48:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我们两个曾经亲密无间{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}We used to read\neach other's thoughts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.36,1:48:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不一样了，是吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It's not the same, is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.23,1:48:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 不太一样  - 呃{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Not quite.  - Hmph.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.04,1:48:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 可看上去…  - 我知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- It doesn't seem...  - I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.58,1:48:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}不知是怎么回事，每当我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I don't know what happens to me.\nWhenever I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.45,1:48:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}没有结婚戒指{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No wedding ring, I see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.88,1:48:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 没有  - 我还以为那位…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- No.  - Well, I thought at the...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.89,1:48:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}昨晚剧院 那位？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Last night, the show?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.46,1:48:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他不是，他不过是，不是…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}No, no.\nHe was just... No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.30,1:48:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我不是故意冒犯你的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I didn't mean to offend you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.37,1:48:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 嗯  - 你的情况怎么样，尼基？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Hmph.  - How's everything with you, Nickie?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.74,1:49:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 噢，想起来问了？  - 嗯哼{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Oh, you can ask questions?  - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.81,1:49:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}应该说昨晚碰见你之前\n一切都还顺利{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Well, I thought everything was fine\nuntil I saw you last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.21,1:49:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我知道你我之间一定出现了隔阂…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Then I knew there must be\nsomething between us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.38,1:49:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}说不定隔着大海\n所以我就买了张船票{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}even if it's only an ocean,\nso I bought myself a ticket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.35,1:49:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，你要去旅行了？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, you're... sailing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.32,1:49:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}今晚就走{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.83,1:49:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你很快活是吗？  - 是的，是的{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And you're happy, aren't you?  - Yes, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.37,1:49:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 你呢？你怎么样？  - 不知道{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And you?  - I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.50,1:49:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我很担心将来\n担心人们对我的议论{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I'm worried about the future.\nI don't know what people will think.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.97,1:49:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他们会说“他跑了，那个古怪的画家{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}They'll say,\n"There he goes, the mad painter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.61,1:49:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他准是中邪了\n他不喜欢女人”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}There's something the matter with him.\nHe doesn't like women."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.41,1:49:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 人们为什么这么说呢？  - 为什么？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- Why would people say that?  - Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.61,1:49:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}因为他走遍了全世界\n每碰见一个女人他就问…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Because he sails the seven seas\nand to every woman he meets he says...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.58,1:49:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}“六个月以后你会在哪儿？”{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}"Where will you be\nin six months?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.59,1:49:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 她们去赴约了吗？  - 都去了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- And they're there?  - Everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.66,1:49:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}金字塔的塔尖 大教堂的顶楼 埃菲尔铁塔{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Tops of pyramids, the domes\nof cathedrals, the Eiffel Tower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.49,1:49:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}他约的地方越来越高{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}He still tries\nto keep them up high.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.59,1:49:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}- 而且总让姑娘白等  - 没错，等啊，等啊，等啊{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}- He keeps them waiting.  - Sure. Waiting, waiting, waiting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.80,1:50:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这么长时间他在哪儿？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And where is he\nall this time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.17,1:50:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}在等待{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Waiting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.14,1:50:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}尼基，你不能老这样等待下去{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But you can't\ngo on like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.34,1:50:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你不该这么做，哦，我真想说声你错了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It isn't right for you.\nOh, I wish I could say you were wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.21,1:50:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我错过一次{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I was once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.28,1:50:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}聊点儿别的怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}How'd you like to\nchange the subject?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.29,1:50:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}当然可以，我很愿意，圣诞快乐{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Yes, yes, I'd love to.\nMerry Christmas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.79,1:50:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}噢，我忘了这碴儿了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, I almost forgot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.43,1:50:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}六个月前，谁能想到我们今天…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Now, six months ago,\nwho'd have thought...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.83,1:50:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}会在温暖的壁炉前\n共度圣诞节呢？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}we'd be spending Christmas together\nin front of a nice warm fire?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.50,1:50:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我给你带了件礼物{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I brought you a present.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.80,1:50:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，谢谢…真抱歉，我没有礼物给你{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, thank you.\nI... I'm sorry. I... don't have one for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.97,1:50:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我…我没想到会有今天{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I... didn't think\nI'd be seeing you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.48,1:50:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我不是来要礼物的\n这件也算不上圣诞礼物{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}That's all right. I didn't expect one.\nThat isn't really a Christmas present.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.16,1:51:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，难怪我的信都给退回来了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh, that's why\nmy letters came back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.90,1:51:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我想把它寄给你\n可我今天才知道你的地址{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I would have sent it to you,\nbut I didn't know your address until today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.41,1:51:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她想把它送给你，记得吗？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She wanted you\nto have it, remember?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.71,1:51:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}所以，呃，我就是为了这个才来的…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So, uh, well, that's\nthe, uh, reason I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.80,1:51:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见，特瑞{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good-bye, Terry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.33,1:51:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}再见，尼基{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Good-bye, Nickie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.72,1:52:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我画过你围着这披肩的肖像{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, I painted you\nlike that with the shawl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.59,1:52:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你看见该多好\n库尔贝说那张画得最好了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I wish you could have seen it.\nCourbet said it was one of my best.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.63,1:52:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我非常珍视它{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I didn't think\nI could ever part with it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.63,1:52:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可是，永远留在身边又不太合适…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}But, well, there was no reason\nto keep it any longer, and, uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.47,1:52:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我舍不得把它卖掉\n因为我…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I couldn't take money for it,\nbecause, well, you know...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.94,1:52:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}有一次，库尔贝说一位年轻的姑娘来到了画廊\n她喜欢那幅画{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}So, uh, Courbet told me a young woman\ncame into the gallery, and, uh, she liked it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.38,1:52:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}她看出了那幅画的内涵\n我就让库尔贝把画送给她了…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She saw in it what I'd hoped you'd see,\nso I told Courbet to give it to her...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.89,1:52:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}因为她说她没有钱，不仅没有钱而且是个…呃…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}because, uh, he said she didn't have any money,\nand not only that, she was, uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.86,1:52:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}是个…{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}She was...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.83,1:52:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}反正我让他把画送给她了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Anyway, I told him\nto give it to her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.24,1:52:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}库尔贝说她很想要那幅画\n噢，我说得太多了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Courbet said she wanted it so badly and,\nuh, so I told him to give it to her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.81,1:52:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}可能是因为今天是圣诞节的缘故{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}You know, it's the, uh,\nChristmas season and all that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.71,1:53:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦，你能理解我的心情{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}And, uh, you know me.\nHolly in my heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.58,1:53:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}亲爱的，别这么看着我{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Darling, don't look\nat me like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.45,1:53:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}你为什么不告诉我？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Why didn't you tell me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.72,1:53:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}如果这种事不可避免\n为什么偏偏是你？{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}If it had to happen to one of us,\nwhy did it have to be you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.59,1:53:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}哦{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.93,1:53:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}这不能怨别人，只怪我自己{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}It was nobody's fault\nbut my own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.07,1:54:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord3\pos(192,286)\3c&H804000&}我只顾仰望大厦了{\r}\N{\fnTimes New Roman\pos(192,286)\3c&H404000&}I-I was looking up.{\r}
